{"tid":334810,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"其實到底足球有咩好睇?","createTime":"2017-07-25T05:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-25T09:22:50.000Z","uid":46400,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0c1c5083d83321460c1a72dc2d15ac72f192690b","tid":334810,"uid":46400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"無論係做野定係正常社交，去到邊都有人講波，一講就圍左爐係咁講完全答唔到嗲。之後我真係返屋企睇左幾場，都係覺得好無聊。90分鐘係到睇住班友係到追住個波有咩好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"3bb9630a25194a2a1d22cf2189e38a3e92bdc84f","tid":334810,"uid":92072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:32:47.000Z","msg":"你冇興趣同唔識欣賞姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果真係咁無聊世界上就唔會有咁多人睇啦<br />\n睇得幾場就批死無聊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd1621d8723be2c489ac9c3cbc3e5514ce208a20","tid":334810,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:37:44.000Z","msg":"當你愛一隊波後就會有唔同睇法"},{"pid":"79a1dfd16e73a191be12a8b55ff1f7aa19b0ec4a","tid":334810,"uid":34490,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:50:11.000Z","msg":"90分鐘淨係望住個波證明係你唔識睇"},{"pid":"ed22bd1a9fa782d974c62e4328a89d618763432a","tid":334810,"uid":128863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T05:57:32.000Z","msg":"如果將足球成場賽事當戲咁睇。<br />\n<br />\n你就會愛上足球。<br />\n<br />\n因為一場賽事未完結。咩都有可能發生"},{"pid":"0abad48efade31e27eb42c2283bf90a720fd7b52","tid":334810,"uid":120393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:14:15.000Z","msg":"因為睇足球唔係淨係睇個九十分鐘場上發生嘅野"},{"pid":"b8c16f91cbeb1ba904e8f544d9a4a71c0a8a09cc","tid":334810,"uid":111648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T06:16:16.000Z","msg":"真男人既野 你點會明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96350dbf822220b0a3d05b329f2e89468ff